Attachments
precis:
Amendment to certain Orders in Council which will authorize the
reimbursement of actual and reasonable travel expenses incurred outside
Canada by the members of three Royal Commissions, namely:
  1. The Royal Commission on Reproductive Technologies
  2. The Royal Commission of National Passenger Transportation
  3. The Royal Commission on Electoral Reform and Party Financing
